dct_title_s: Lincoln, New Jersey now Middlesex Borough
dct_description_sm: Map of Lincoln, N.J. (present day Middlesex Borough) includes numbered residential blocks and lettered industrial lots along Lincoln Boulevard with the names of some businesses. The Lehigh Valley railroad line and depot and the Central Railroad of New Jersey line are also featured prominently.
